original_title: Max Dolcelli: Funny Is All Around Us
overview: Max Dolcelli has appeared just about everywhere and done just about everything a comedian can do, performing in comedy clubs and comedy festivals in the U.S. and Canada, casinos and clubs in Las Vegas, Atlantic City, and the Bahamas, at corporate events and on cruise ships, and on television and radio.
title: Max Dolcelli: Funny Is All Around Us
